		{
			"type": "paragraph",
			"children": [
				{
					"type": "text",
					"text": "The Indonesian island full of surprises. Bali is a beautiful island representing almost a tropical paradise. On this relatively small but diverse island, you can find almost everything. Iconic views with majestic volcanoes in the background, waterfalls almost around every corner, kitschy green rice fields with coconut palms, beautiful Hindu temples, clean beaches, and blue sea. Surfers, scuba diving enthusiasts, or mountain hikers will find their own paradise here."
				}
			]
		},
