					"text": "Bali",
					"url": "https://lowcost-traveling.com/destinace/bali/"
				},
				{
					"type": "text",
					"text": ". Despite being close to each other, they are definitely not the same. On the contrary, it’s said that Lombok resembles Bali from 30 years ago. There are places on the island where tourists are seen only occasionally, and several areas where tourism is just beginning. The island is quieter, less crowded, and represents Indonesia more authentically. Instead of colorful temples, you’ll find mosques; instead of restaurants, street food vendors; and in place of civilization, wilderness."
				}
			]
		},
