		{
			"type": "paragraph",
			"children": [
				{
					"type": "text",
					"text": "High mountains and dense jungle, rice fields, and poor people living their simple lives. Ancient cities, Buddhist temples, as well as ubiquitous motorbikes, modern cities, luxurious cars, and massive modern buildings. That’s Vietnam, a land of contrasts."
				}
			]
		},
